<!-- 著名剧目 -->
<section class="py-16 bg-white">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-[clamp(1.8rem,5vw,2.5rem)] text-title mb-4">著名剧目</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">粤剧历经数百年发展，留下了许多经典剧目。</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <div class="bg-neutral-50 rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-md transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-lg">
        <div class="h-64 overflow-hidden">
          <img src="assets\images\culture\yueju-play1.jpg" alt="帝女花" class="w-full h-full object-cover">
        </div>
        <div class="p-6">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-secondary mb-3">《帝女花》</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">《帝女花》是粤剧的经典剧目之一，由唐涤生编剧，讲述了明末崇祯皇帝之女长平公主与驸马周世显的爱情故事，剧情悲怆动人，是粤剧的代表作。</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="bg-neutral-50 rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-md transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-lg">
        <div class="h-64 overflow-hidden">
          <img src="assets\images\culture\yueju-play2.jpg" alt="紫钗记" class="w-full h-full object-cover">
        </div>
        <div class="p-6">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-secondary mb-3">《紫钗记》</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">《紫钗记》改编自唐代传奇《霍小玉传》，讲述了才子李益与歌妓霍小玉的爱情故事，剧情曲折动人，音乐优美，是粤剧舞台上的常演剧目。</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="bg-neutral-50 rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-md transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-lg">
        <div class="h-64 overflow-hidden">
          <img src="assets\images\culture\yueju-play3.jpg" alt="牡丹亭" class="w-full h-full object-cover">
        </div>
        <div class="p-6">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-secondary mb-3">《牡丹亭》</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">《牡丹亭》改编自明代汤显祖的同名传奇，讲述了杜丽娘与柳梦梅的爱情故事，剧情奇幻浪漫，是粤剧的经典剧目之一。</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

