        </div>
        <div class="p-6">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-secondary mb-3">红线女</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">红线女是粤剧艺术的一代宗师，创立了"红派"艺术，对粤剧的发展产生了深远影响，代表作有《搜书院》《关汉卿》等。</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-md transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-lg">
        <div class="h-80 overflow-hidden">
          <img src="assets\images\culture\yueju-actor2.jpg" alt="马师曾" class="w-full h-full object-cover">
        </div>
        <div class="p-6">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-secondary mb-3">马师曾</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">马师曾是粤剧著名演员，创立了"马派"艺术，以丑生表演著称，演技精湛，代表作有《苦凤莺怜》《审死官》等。</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-md transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-lg">
        <div class="h-80 overflow-hidden">
          <img src="assets\images\culture\yueju-actor3.jpg" alt="薛觉先" class="w-full h-full object-cover">
        </div>
        <div class="p-6">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-secondary mb-3">薛觉先</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">薛觉先是粤剧"薛派"艺术的创始人，表演风格文武兼备，唱做俱佳，代表作有《胡不归》《王昭君》等。</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-md transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-lg">
        <div class="h-80 overflow-hidden">
          <img src="assets\images\culture\yueju-actor4.jpg" alt="白雪仙" class="w-full h-full object-cover">
        </div>
        <div class="p-6">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-secondary mb-3">白雪仙</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">白雪仙是粤剧著名花旦，与任剑辉合作多年，形成了独特的表演风格，代表作有《帝女花》《紫钗记》等。</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

